<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='322000' id='t-322000'>(Laughter)</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='327000' id='t-327000'>So anyway, we found activity in three brain regions.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='329000' id='t-329000'>We found activity in the brain region,</span>
