<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='518000' id='t-518000'>And indeed, it has all of the characteristics of addiction.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='521000' id='t-521000'>You focus on the person, you obsessively think about them,</span>
