 9:41
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='570000' id='t-570000'>I would also like to tell the world that animals love.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='574000' id='t-574000'>There's not an animal on this planet</span>
