<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='636000' id='t-636000'>People have often asked me whether</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='641000' id='t-641000'>what I know about love has spoiled it for me.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='644000' id='t-644000'>And I just simply say, &quot;Hardly.&quot;</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='646000' id='t-646000'>You can know every single ingredient in a piece of chocolate cake,</span>
