<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='721000' id='t-721000'>and I'm only going to say it for a second, and then end --</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='724000' id='t-724000'>is, why do you fall in love with one person, rather than another?</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='728000' id='t-728000'>I never would have even thought to think of this,</span>
