<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='846000' id='t-846000'>So, I will close with this. These are my older people.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='852000' id='t-852000'>Faulkner once said, &quot;The past is not dead,</span>
